.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-REMOTE-PCT-BOTTOM10" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-remote-pct-bottom10 \- FEAT-2740 channel-remote-pct-bottom10 verb
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-remote-pct-bottom10
.SH DESCRIPTION
Show the bottom 10 channels by remote balance percentage (lowest remote balance relative to channel capacity).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN with key \fBbottom10_by_remote_pct\fR containing an array of channel objects with their remote balance percentage.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
